  "description": "Nightshade family — ~103 genera, ~2,700 species. Diagnostic 5-merous flowers, berry or capsule fruit, tropane and steroidal alkaloid chemistry. Native to South America, includes food crops (tomato, potato, peppers) and highly toxic medicinal plants (belladonna, datura).",
